  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM1.3">
<l>emmāṇ piṉaya ṉāṉku nāviṉālum</l>
<l>eṭuttētti īriraṇṭu mukamuṅ koṇ</l>
<l>ṭemmāṭu meḻiṟkaṇka ḷeṭṭi ṉōṭun</l>
<l>toḻutētti yiṉitiṟaiñca niṉṟa cempoṉ</l>
<l>ṉammāṉṟaṉ malarkkamalak koppūḻ tōṉṟa</l>
<l>vaṇiyaraṅkat taravaṇaiyiṟ paḷḷi koḷḷum</l>
<l>ammāṉṟa ṉaṭiyiṇaikkī ḻalarkaḷi ṭṭaṅ</l>
<l>kaṭiyavarō ṭeṉṟukolō vaṇuku nāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When is the day that [I shall] approach that place, along with the servants,</l>
<l>placing blossoms beneath the pair of feet of</l>
<l>the Lord, who sleeps on His serpent-bed in decorated Raṅgam,</l>
<l rend="indent">as his navel with the lotus flower appears,</l>
<l>the red gold[-like] Lord who stood so that</l>
<l rend="indent">Aja, who is in all ways honourable, pleasingly bows down,</l>
<l rend="indent">speaking highly of [Him], praising [Him] with all [of his] four tongues,</l>
<l rend="indent">worshipping [and] constantly praising [Him] with [his] eight graceful eyes</l>
<l rend="indent">[that see in] all directions and with [his] four faces?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
